snippet.title: Venice 2089 - Official Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
Meet the characters and get a look at the world of Venice 2089, a game set in an explorative and narrative-driven game set in a whole new Venice, now left uninhabited due to the effects of global warming, seen through the eyes of a bored, apathetic teen. 

A Kickstarter for the game launches on June 2020, and a demo for the game is available now on Steam.
